WEBVTT

01:36.200 --> 01:37.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL OF THE SAME NAME
BY ZHU YI ON WWW.JJWXC.NET

01:42.800 --> 01:43.640
Why's the power out?

01:44.600 --> 01:46.800
Alright. Everyone, quiet down.

01:46.880 --> 01:48.520
I can't find anything.

01:48.600 --> 01:50.120
- There's a ghost!
- Who?

01:50.200 --> 01:51.400
Who's there?

01:53.960 --> 01:55.160
Are you crazy?

01:55.240 --> 01:56.600
Why are you pretending
to be a ghost at this hour?

01:56.680 --> 01:57.520
Why did you push me?

01:57.600 --> 01:58.800
What are you doing?

01:58.880 --> 02:00.160
You don't even take a moment
to check yourself.

02:00.240 --> 02:01.080
You're the one who looks like a ghost.

02:01.160 --> 02:02.080
Say that again!

02:02.160 --> 02:03.760
- She's no longer just a pretty face.
- Alright.

02:03.840 --> 02:04.800
It's fine.

02:04.880 --> 02:06.720
Alright. Everyone, stop causing a scene.

02:06.800 --> 02:08.880
The power won't come back anytime soon.
You can go back for now.

02:08.960 --> 02:11.120
- Why were you making such a fuss?
- Alright, stop it.

02:11.200 --> 02:12.040
What are you staring at?

02:12.120 --> 02:13.960
Let's go. Everyone, disperse.

02:14.040 --> 02:15.040
I'm looking at the moon.

02:15.880 --> 02:18.280
Really? You're looking
at that Pretty Face Wen, aren't you?

02:18.800 --> 02:20.120
She's your romantic interest, right?

02:53.280 --> 02:54.240
The power's back on.

03:04.520 --> 03:05.520
What are you looking at?

03:07.720 --> 03:09.000
My romantic interest.

03:12.280 --> 03:13.840
You heard that?

03:15.040 --> 03:17.640
Su Haoan has a big mouth.
He's just talking nonsense.

03:22.080 --> 03:24.720
This should be… a good word, right?

03:32.520 --> 03:33.520
Thank you.

03:42.120 --> 03:43.000
Can't you see it?

03:43.760 --> 03:45.280
I can. It's clearer this way.

04:09.160 --> 04:14.240
EIGHT YEARS LATER

04:19.920 --> 04:21.000
Lin.

04:21.079 --> 04:22.200
Fan.

04:24.280 --> 04:26.400
What's wrong? Why do you look so messy?

04:27.480 --> 04:30.000
Something happened at my old place.

04:30.080 --> 04:32.680
Sorry, Lin. Sorry to bother you so late.

04:33.200 --> 04:35.520
It's okay. Hurry, come in.

04:44.760 --> 04:45.880
Fan.

04:46.400 --> 04:48.840
I forgot to tell you…

04:49.720 --> 04:52.560
No cats allowed. I'm allergic to cat fur.

04:55.920 --> 04:57.920
Can I keep it in the room?

04:58.960 --> 05:00.920
Is it okay if I put it in the room, Lin?

05:01.440 --> 05:02.600
Don't worry. It won't run around.

05:02.680 --> 05:04.280
But the fur will fly everywhere.

05:04.360 --> 05:07.400
Every time you open and close the door,
the air circulates

05:08.080 --> 05:09.480
and the fur just floats out.

05:10.920 --> 05:13.320
Forget it. We'll deal with it today.

05:14.560 --> 05:17.120
Tomorrow,
you can send it to your friend's place.

05:25.240 --> 05:27.520
By the way, I forgot to ask you.

05:27.600 --> 05:29.080
How did you get back?

05:29.600 --> 05:31.920
I saw Sang Yan. He gave me a ride.

05:32.680 --> 05:35.280
You asked him to give you a ride?

05:37.120 --> 05:38.800
He didn't offer to take you?

05:39.480 --> 05:41.000
He didn't need to, right?

05:41.080 --> 05:43.480
Don't do that next time.

05:43.560 --> 05:46.200
He must be really happy now.

05:46.280 --> 05:48.640
He's probably bragging to his friends.

05:48.720 --> 05:51.240
Look, you're his romantic interest.

05:51.320 --> 05:52.560
He couldn't get you back then.

05:52.640 --> 05:54.960
And now? Now, you're the one chasing him.

05:55.040 --> 05:56.400
He probably thinks,

05:56.480 --> 05:59.800
"I'll play with you for a while.
Once I get bored, I'll dump you."

05:59.880 --> 06:03.280
Take my word. Nowadays,
rich guys all follow the same routine.

06:03.360 --> 06:05.400
Or don't blame me
for not warning you later.

06:06.160 --> 06:07.280
Got it.

06:08.240 --> 06:09.960
I've stuck the important notes
on the fridge.

06:10.040 --> 06:11.080
Remember to read them.

06:11.920 --> 06:12.960
Good night.

06:14.280 --> 06:15.560
Good night, Lin.

06:23.440 --> 06:27.120
CO-LIVING NOTES

06:42.480 --> 06:45.040
NEWS REPORTING VEHICLE

06:52.600 --> 06:54.000
I'll take this, Yifan.

06:57.600 --> 06:59.600
- You've been waiting for a while, huh?
- Here are some flowers for you.

06:59.680 --> 07:01.240
Thank you.

07:01.320 --> 07:03.600
And a gift for you. Get in the car.

07:06.720 --> 07:08.760
Looks like she's found
another long-term meal ticket.

07:21.080 --> 07:23.160
UPTOWN FLOWER CITY

07:24.080 --> 07:25.720
Be good at Qiao's place.

07:26.520 --> 07:29.120
Don't worry. I'll definitely feed it
until it's nice and plump.

07:31.800 --> 07:33.000
Alright, no more.

07:33.520 --> 07:35.720
Enough. You greedy cat.

07:35.800 --> 07:36.640
Come on.

07:36.720 --> 07:39.560
- Here are its toys and other stuff.
- Haven't we already made it really clear?

07:39.640 --> 07:41.440
- If anything happens, give me a call.
- We've broken up.

07:41.520 --> 07:43.640
You're not my boyfriend,
and I'm not your girlfriend.

07:43.720 --> 07:46.080
- I'll see what she looks like.
- Qiao.

07:46.880 --> 07:48.680
Qiao. No!

07:48.760 --> 07:50.880
But when we had dinner that day,
we already talked about it.

07:50.960 --> 07:54.440
You're great, and I'm great too.
So, we should just break up peacefully.

07:54.520 --> 07:56.640
No. What do you want?
Didn't I already buy you everything?

07:56.720 --> 07:58.960
I bought the bags you wanted,
even the most hard-to-find ones.

07:59.040 --> 08:01.600
I don't care about those bags.
Take those bags with you.

08:02.600 --> 08:05.000
Those bags are yours. I gave them to you.

08:05.080 --> 08:05.960
Throw them away or sell them.
It's up to you.

08:06.040 --> 08:09.120
Fine. Then I'll sell them to you.

08:09.200 --> 08:12.000
I'll sell them cheap, half price.
I'll send them back to you right now.

08:12.080 --> 08:13.360
Don't forget to pay me half the money!

08:14.880 --> 08:17.040
Fan!

08:18.080 --> 08:19.040
Lin.

08:22.760 --> 08:24.360
I need to pack some bags.

08:24.440 --> 08:26.920
Can you help me call a courier later?
I'll give you the address.

08:29.880 --> 08:31.880
- Can you deliver it?
- I can.

08:31.960 --> 08:33.840
Okay. Alright.

08:34.480 --> 08:36.360
Lin, my friend can help you deliver.

08:36.440 --> 08:38.000
You can just place the order
on your phone.

08:38.080 --> 08:40.200
- Really?
- Yeah, I can help you with that.

08:40.280 --> 08:42.760
- They'll be delivered tonight.
- Thank you, pretty girl.

08:43.400 --> 08:46.440
- Are you a courier?
- Pretty much.

08:47.480 --> 08:49.360
- Is this the address?
- Yes.

08:49.440 --> 08:50.280
Alright.

08:50.360 --> 08:51.480
It's done.

08:52.520 --> 08:53.520
Thanks.

08:53.600 --> 08:55.840
- I'll help you pack.
- Okay, let's go!

09:00.560 --> 09:01.720
Coming.

09:06.200 --> 09:07.160
Hello.

09:07.920 --> 09:08.760
Lin.

09:09.360 --> 09:10.200
Your boyfriend…

09:10.960 --> 09:12.520
Your ex-boyfriend's here.

09:12.600 --> 09:14.440
- Lin.
- Stay right there!

09:14.960 --> 09:15.960
Don't come over here.

09:16.560 --> 09:18.320
We're not a couple anymore.

09:18.400 --> 09:19.520
I don't care about those bags.

09:20.280 --> 09:21.880
I truly care about our relationship.

09:22.400 --> 09:24.200
I don't care about those bags either.

09:24.280 --> 09:26.000
I really want to return them

09:26.800 --> 09:27.840
to you.

09:27.920 --> 09:29.680
But weren't we just
happily having dinner together?

09:29.760 --> 09:31.920
Don't you understand
what a farewell dinner means?

09:32.440 --> 09:34.000
- Pretty girl!
- Yes!

09:35.120 --> 09:37.280
These are the bags. Just these two boxes.

09:37.360 --> 09:38.200
Alright.

09:39.720 --> 09:42.200
- Help me deliver them there. Right there.
- Okay.

09:42.280 --> 09:45.080
Could you show me
the pick-up code, please?

09:46.320 --> 09:48.360
Sorry. Could you show me
the pick-up code, please?

09:48.440 --> 09:49.320
Only then will the order be completed.

09:52.480 --> 09:53.320
I'm not accepting the order.

09:57.080 --> 09:58.880
Do you know why I bought you bags?

09:58.960 --> 10:00.640
Why I bought you clothes?
Why I bought you whatever you wanted?

10:00.720 --> 10:04.320
Because you can afford to buy them
and I'm qualified to accept them.

10:04.400 --> 10:08.360
During the pursuit,
that's an exchange of goods and services.

10:13.240 --> 10:14.160
That's because I love you.

10:25.080 --> 10:27.600
That word, "love",
of course, can't be weighed or counted.

10:27.680 --> 10:30.800
But it's because I love you
that these bags bear value.

10:30.880 --> 10:34.640
So, now that I don't love you,
do these bags have no value anymore?

10:40.320 --> 10:41.440
Just take them.

10:42.320 --> 10:44.200
Consider it me begging you.

10:45.360 --> 10:46.200
Alright?

10:48.840 --> 10:51.480
By the way, I can actually
deliver them to your door.

11:04.240 --> 11:06.760
1,748…

11:08.040 --> 11:09.120
Alright, thank you.

11:11.560 --> 11:12.680
Please throw these bags away for me.

11:20.880 --> 11:22.840
I'll pay the money. Thirty, right?

11:33.120 --> 11:34.880
Have you heard Wang Linlin is leaving?

11:34.960 --> 11:36.840
Seems like she has landed
a big client in the ad department.

11:36.920 --> 11:39.400
No wonder she took time off
for New Year's Eve.

11:39.480 --> 11:42.280
The last time I saw a car picking her up,
it switched from a Porsche to a Ferrari.

11:43.240 --> 11:44.680
I wish I could drive a Ferrari too.

11:46.160 --> 11:48.080
Your eavesdropping skills are terrible.

11:48.160 --> 11:49.920
Me? What do you mean, eavesdropping?

11:50.000 --> 11:53.680
Aren't the three of us a combo?
What's something I can't hear?

11:53.760 --> 11:55.920
- You two can't leave me out.
- Fine.

11:56.440 --> 11:58.160
What's the point of relying on a man?

11:58.240 --> 11:59.600
Relying on ourselves is the best.

12:00.200 --> 12:01.600
Are you stupid?

12:02.600 --> 12:04.720
You're pregnant
and still breaking up with him?

12:04.800 --> 12:07.760
Before breaking up, shouldn't you at least
try to get some child-support funds?

12:07.840 --> 12:08.840
I'm talking about Lin.

12:08.920 --> 12:10.440
- Why are you dragging me into this?
- Where are the house keys?

12:10.520 --> 12:11.720
Did you forget to leave them for me?

12:11.800 --> 12:13.000
I'm mentioning this for your own good.

12:13.600 --> 12:14.520
Sorry.

12:14.600 --> 12:16.480
Let me know when you have time
and I'll bring them to you.

12:16.560 --> 12:20.280
Think about it.
When your baby's born, don't you

12:20.360 --> 12:21.760
need child-support money?

12:21.840 --> 12:23.240
Don't you need all sorts of things?

12:23.320 --> 12:24.680
All that messy stuff.

12:24.760 --> 12:25.760
Let me tell you,

12:25.840 --> 12:29.960
I am an independent woman
in terms of thoughts and finances.

12:30.040 --> 12:31.520
- I didn't lose them, did I?
- So, don't mind this business.

12:31.600 --> 12:34.120
Listen, I started dating in first grade.

12:34.200 --> 12:36.200
You've had a girlfriend since first grade?

12:36.840 --> 12:38.160
Oh, senior.

12:38.680 --> 12:41.400
Do you know why you're single now?

12:41.480 --> 12:43.000
It's because of a word.

12:43.080 --> 12:44.000
Immaturity.

12:44.080 --> 12:45.560
How do you know I'm single?

12:46.080 --> 12:47.320
I'm still in touch with her.

12:47.400 --> 12:49.760
Who knows,
maybe we'll get married one day.

12:50.800 --> 12:51.880
How are they with him?

12:51.960 --> 12:53.840
Did you purposely leave them with me?

12:53.920 --> 12:56.760
I suggest not using
the same trick a second time.

12:56.840 --> 12:57.960
Why didn't he return them to me
in the first place?

12:58.040 --> 13:01.520
Did he want to take the opportunity
to make a point, saying I'm being clingy?

13:14.720 --> 13:15.680
WEN YIFAN

13:16.640 --> 13:18.120
So, they're at your place?

13:18.200 --> 13:20.560
Let me know when you're free.
I'll go get them.

13:20.640 --> 13:22.320
Sorry for bothering you again.

13:30.800 --> 13:32.680
After work, come over to Overtime.

13:36.440 --> 13:39.080
Do you have time tonight?
Let's have dinner together.

13:39.160 --> 13:41.120
- I have time.
- Me, too.

13:41.200 --> 13:42.920
- Where should we eat?
- Overtime.

13:43.960 --> 13:44.800
So,

13:45.400 --> 13:47.840
is this overtime or dinner?

13:47.920 --> 13:49.920
OVERTIME

13:51.920 --> 13:54.760
Turns out Overtime
is what they call this place.

13:56.160 --> 13:59.440
Looks like this meal
isn't just a casual one.

14:02.920 --> 14:03.960
Thanks.

14:10.200 --> 14:12.720
I won't keep you any longer.
My colleagues are still waiting for me.

14:22.800 --> 14:24.640
Sorry for bothering you so many times.

14:24.720 --> 14:27.000
Let me know when you're free.
I'll treat you to a meal.

14:27.520 --> 14:28.360
I'm free anytime.

14:29.800 --> 14:31.600
How many times do you need to say that?

14:32.160 --> 14:34.080
If I don't agree, you won't give up, huh?

14:38.480 --> 14:39.920
Since you want to treat,

14:40.680 --> 14:42.320
- let's do it tomorrow.
- What do you want to eat?

14:43.000 --> 14:44.040
Anything.

14:45.160 --> 14:47.200
- Any dietary restrictions?
- A lot.

14:47.280 --> 14:49.080
- Hotpot?
- Spicy.

14:49.160 --> 14:50.120
- BBQ?
- Too strong.

14:50.200 --> 14:51.360
- Sichuan food?
- Too spicy.

14:53.320 --> 14:55.880
So, what do you feel like eating?
I'm okay with anything.

14:55.960 --> 14:57.680
- I don't have many restrictions.
- Anything.

15:04.200 --> 15:06.200
Hey! Your house exploded!

15:09.440 --> 15:10.360
Speak properly.

15:10.440 --> 15:11.280
Not your house.

15:11.360 --> 15:12.800
It's the house downstairs that exploded.

15:12.880 --> 15:15.680
Do you know how big the fire is?
Your place almost burned down!

15:16.440 --> 15:18.520
You should come back and take a look!

15:19.200 --> 15:22.080
Could you please call 119 for me? Thanks.

15:24.600 --> 15:26.920
Your house caught fire.
Aren't you going back to check?

15:28.000 --> 15:30.520
I'm not a firefighter. I can't help much.
Why go back?

15:31.760 --> 15:34.880
May I ask where exactly your house is?

15:34.960 --> 15:37.440
- Why?
- I'm thinking of doing a report.

15:41.280 --> 15:43.280
Could you tell me the name of the complex?

15:43.360 --> 15:45.120
Hello, Yifan. I was just looking for you.

15:45.720 --> 15:47.160
There's a fire
in Central South Century City.

15:47.240 --> 15:48.080
I'm heading there right now.

15:48.160 --> 15:49.920
Wait for me there. See you soon.

15:50.440 --> 15:51.480
Central South Century City?

15:52.320 --> 15:54.600
Yes. Central South Century City.

15:54.680 --> 15:56.640
Alright. See you soon.

16:00.320 --> 16:01.520
Mr. Yifan's high school classmate,

16:01.600 --> 16:02.760
don't worry too much.

16:02.840 --> 16:05.560
Our report this time
will be comprehensive and objective.

16:05.640 --> 16:07.640
We'll help you defend your rights
and recover your losses.

16:09.280 --> 16:10.680
I think it should be this way.

16:15.040 --> 16:16.200
Hello, Officer.

16:16.280 --> 16:18.560
I'd like to ask,
where are the affected households?

16:18.640 --> 16:19.680
Over there.

16:19.760 --> 16:21.200
- Those two?
- Yes.

16:21.280 --> 16:22.160
Alright, thank you.

16:22.240 --> 16:23.480
Come this way.

16:24.160 --> 16:25.960
You two go interview
the rescue personnel first.

16:26.040 --> 16:27.560
Don't disturb their work.

16:28.680 --> 16:29.960
Okay. Come on.

16:30.720 --> 16:33.560
- Hello. Are you a resident here?
- Yes.

16:33.640 --> 16:36.240
We're from the First News program
of Nanwu TV Station.

16:36.320 --> 16:37.400
Can we interview you?

16:37.480 --> 16:38.440
Sure.

16:38.520 --> 16:41.240
- Which floor do you live on?
- We live on the seventh floor.

16:41.760 --> 16:44.320
I heard a loud bang outside.
It startled me.

16:44.400 --> 16:46.240
I thought it was fireworks.

16:46.320 --> 16:49.360
Someone said
a resident on the eighth floor

16:49.440 --> 16:52.360
charged an electric bike
and caused the fire.

16:52.440 --> 16:54.720
The fire spread
straight to the ninth floor.

16:54.800 --> 16:56.520
The resident on the ninth floor

16:57.480 --> 16:58.640
was really unlucky.

16:59.640 --> 17:01.880
May I ask, is the resident
on the ninth floor at the scene?

17:02.720 --> 17:03.720
And the name?

17:03.800 --> 17:05.000
I think…

17:05.599 --> 17:07.359
it's… a handsome guy named Sang.

17:08.640 --> 17:10.920
Is he nearby?

17:12.720 --> 17:14.359
- That's him.
- Yes.

17:14.440 --> 17:16.359
Got it. Thanks.

17:18.160 --> 17:19.000
Hello.

17:19.640 --> 17:20.760
Sorry to disturb you.

17:20.839 --> 17:23.319
Are you the affected resident
from the ninth floor?

17:24.119 --> 17:25.160
Yes.

17:25.240 --> 17:29.880
I'm sorry to hear that your place
was hit the hardest by the fire, correct?

17:29.960 --> 17:30.800
So what?

17:30.880 --> 17:32.840
Do you have any compensation claims?

17:32.920 --> 17:33.840
Through our interview,

17:33.920 --> 17:35.000
we can assist you
in defending your rights.

17:35.080 --> 17:36.960
What I mean is,
there's nothing valuable in my home,

17:37.040 --> 17:38.040
so it's fine.

17:38.120 --> 17:40.680
So, do you have any requests?

17:40.760 --> 17:41.680
No.

17:42.200 --> 17:43.640
Sir! Wait up.

17:43.720 --> 17:46.240
Well… I totally understand
how you feel right now.

17:46.320 --> 17:48.600
After all, it's a fire.
But it's fine you're safe.

17:48.680 --> 17:50.320
I hope through our interview,

17:50.400 --> 17:52.560
we can remind everyone
to be cautious about electric bike fires.

17:53.480 --> 17:55.440
Is there anything you'd like to say now?

18:02.680 --> 18:05.680
I'm happy.
I hope you can be as happy as I am.

18:10.560 --> 18:11.920
What happened to him?

18:12.000 --> 18:13.360
He's probably been shaken up.

18:17.040 --> 18:19.400
Hello. We're from Nanwu TV.

18:19.480 --> 18:22.640
I heard that your place
was hit the hardest by the fire, correct?

18:22.720 --> 18:23.880
So what?

18:24.760 --> 18:26.800
What I mean is,
there's nothing valuable in my home,

18:26.880 --> 18:27.720
so it's fine.

18:28.320 --> 18:30.080
So, do you have any requests?

18:30.760 --> 18:33.520
I'm happy.
I hope you can be as happy as I am.

18:36.040 --> 18:37.320
SANG YAN; HAPPY NEW YEAR!
IT'S FINE IF YOU'RE NOT HAPPY

18:42.280 --> 18:45.440
Yifan, your classmate
is both unlucky and amazing.

18:46.080 --> 18:48.520
His house got burned down like that,
yet he's so calm.

18:48.600 --> 18:49.640
Go comfort him.

18:49.720 --> 18:50.800
Let him talk to the property management

18:50.880 --> 18:52.520
and the insurance company
about compensation.

18:52.600 --> 18:53.960
Don't be too sad.

18:54.920 --> 18:56.680
He doesn't look that sad though.

18:57.600 --> 18:59.280
How do you know what he is thinking?

19:00.080 --> 19:02.200
By the way, Ms. Qian's looking for you.

19:02.280 --> 19:03.720
Go see her. Hurry.

19:05.000 --> 19:06.040
I'll go first.

19:19.400 --> 19:20.600
Morning, Lin.

19:21.120 --> 19:22.000
Morning.

19:22.080 --> 19:23.080
You're up so early.

19:23.160 --> 19:24.560
No, I just came back.

19:24.640 --> 19:26.600
I was out all night, totally exhausted.

19:28.320 --> 19:30.480
Do you still have the energy
to work today?

19:31.000 --> 19:33.760
Are you trying to kill me?
How could I have the energy to work?

19:34.280 --> 19:37.400
- So, you're not going to work today?
- Not planning to.

19:37.920 --> 19:40.200
Don't you think
working every day is so tiring?

19:40.920 --> 19:42.200
I'm okay.

19:42.720 --> 19:43.760
You are No.1.

19:44.560 --> 19:45.480
Fan.

19:46.920 --> 19:49.120
Come sit. I need to talk to you.

19:54.400 --> 19:56.320
Promise me first that you won't get mad.

19:56.960 --> 20:01.400
As I just put it,
this job is really exhausting.

20:01.480 --> 20:02.920
And the pay is so little.

20:03.000 --> 20:05.480
A month's salary
doesn't even cover the cost of a bag.

20:05.560 --> 20:08.240
I have been fed up with it.
I can't keep going like this.

20:08.760 --> 20:09.960
I'm thinking of quitting today.

20:10.960 --> 20:13.320
My cousin said
he's introduced me to a new job.

20:13.400 --> 20:14.560
It's in Gaozikou.

20:15.960 --> 20:16.920
So…

20:17.960 --> 20:19.240
Just wait a second, Lin.

20:19.760 --> 20:22.200
Fan! Are you mad?

20:22.280 --> 20:23.200
I…

20:25.440 --> 20:28.480
It's a bit far from here, you know.

20:32.400 --> 20:34.560
So, you're not planning
to live here anymore?

20:35.080 --> 20:37.200
I didn't know it was this far in advance.

20:37.280 --> 20:39.240
If I could stay here,
I would definitely stay here.

20:39.960 --> 20:42.800
I'll definitely find you
a very reliable new roommate.

20:42.880 --> 20:43.880
But…

20:45.440 --> 20:47.520
But I just moved in,
and now you're leaving?

20:47.600 --> 20:49.600
How am I supposed
to handle the rent on my own, Lin?

20:50.320 --> 20:52.360
I won't take the deposit back.
Consider it as covering one month's rent.

20:52.440 --> 20:54.000
You can live here without worries.

20:54.080 --> 20:55.640
You want a female roommate, right?

20:56.240 --> 20:57.960
I'll definitely ask for your opinion.

20:58.040 --> 21:00.760
If you don't agree,
I won't let her step foot in this house.

21:34.680 --> 21:37.080
Little girl, you're really something.

21:37.160 --> 21:38.920
You've made such a big deal out of this.

21:39.000 --> 21:40.480
You've forced everyone
to cancel their leases.

21:40.560 --> 21:41.800
Everyone's gone.

21:41.880 --> 21:42.920
Did the fat uncle move too?

21:43.000 --> 21:44.440
It must be related
to that incident with you.

21:44.520 --> 21:45.840
It's all your fault.

21:45.920 --> 21:49.120
Was it my fault?
The police have the record.

21:49.200 --> 21:50.440
You can check it out.

21:50.520 --> 21:54.120
With the New Year approaching,
it's not easy to rent this place out.

21:54.640 --> 21:56.160
Who's going to pay for the loss?

22:00.920 --> 22:04.040
Our TV station is very interested
in reporting on housing safety.

22:04.560 --> 22:07.840
If I hadn't kept quiet, your house
would have been in the morning news.

22:10.080 --> 22:12.760
Or do you want your house
to be in the news?

22:13.480 --> 22:15.480
Getting a little publicity
might make it easier to rent.

22:20.200 --> 22:21.600
I'm leaving now.

22:50.600 --> 22:51.560
Why is the door unlocked?

23:55.760 --> 23:57.120
Is anyone home?

23:57.200 --> 23:59.000
Hello. I need to report a theft.
Someone's broken into my house!

24:01.880 --> 24:03.600
Uptown Flower City.
Building 7, Apartment 1701.

24:04.720 --> 24:06.320
I don't even know
how many people are in there…

24:13.120 --> 24:15.600
Sorry, I mistook him for a thief.

24:16.400 --> 24:17.480
Yes. Sorry.

24:18.680 --> 24:20.040
It's safe now.

24:21.880 --> 24:22.720
So sorry.

24:25.000 --> 24:26.040
Hey, why are you here?

24:28.040 --> 24:30.320
Same here. Why are you here?

24:30.400 --> 24:32.840
This is my home.
What do you think I'm doing here?

24:41.080 --> 24:42.000
Hey, Lin.

24:42.520 --> 24:45.720
Who is it? I've already gone to bed.

24:45.800 --> 24:47.000
It's Wen Yifan.

24:47.600 --> 24:49.040
What's the matter?

24:49.120 --> 24:50.440
Make it short.

24:50.520 --> 24:53.680
I want to ask you something.
Did you give the keys to someone else?

24:53.760 --> 24:55.480
You mean Sang Yan?

24:57.120 --> 25:01.360
I can hardly find someone to replace me.

25:01.440 --> 25:04.040
If it drags on until next month,
you'll have to pay the full rent.

25:04.760 --> 25:06.320
I'm just worried about you.

25:06.400 --> 25:08.600
- Is that so?
- Yes.

25:08.680 --> 25:11.360
- How will you thank me, bro?
- Su Haoan, are you crazy?

25:11.440 --> 25:13.440
It's your first day
living with your Goddess Wen

25:13.520 --> 25:15.400
and you're this angry?
Is that really necessary?

25:15.480 --> 25:18.600
Is your brain still underdeveloped,
or has it never developed?

25:18.680 --> 25:19.680
She's a girl.

25:19.760 --> 25:21.400
Is it appropriate for a guy like me
to live with her?

25:21.480 --> 25:22.520
We agreed, right?

25:22.600 --> 25:24.160
You're supposed to find me
a female roommate, Lin.

25:24.240 --> 25:26.680
What's the big deal about male or female?

25:26.760 --> 25:28.560
You asked me to help you find a place,

25:28.640 --> 25:30.560
so I asked you
what your requirements were.

25:30.640 --> 25:31.960
You said just somewhere
near Uptown Flower City would be fine.

25:32.040 --> 25:34.240
Do you two have some history?

25:34.320 --> 25:35.200
No.

25:35.280 --> 25:37.440
Then, could you ask your girlfriend
to let me know in advance?

25:37.520 --> 25:39.680
And tell her too.
That way, we can be prepared.

25:39.760 --> 25:41.360
She treated me like a thief
and even called the police.

25:41.440 --> 25:42.920
- Can you imagine that?
- We agreed, right?

25:43.000 --> 25:44.600
You're supposed to find me
a female roommate, Lin.

25:44.680 --> 25:48.680
Fan, let's talk about it
tomorrow morning, alright?

25:49.200 --> 25:51.440
I really need to sleep now.

25:51.520 --> 25:52.520
Hello?

26:34.480 --> 26:36.480
- Can we talk?
- Okay.

26:44.800 --> 26:46.240
This…

26:46.760 --> 26:48.320
might be a misunderstanding.

26:48.400 --> 26:49.320
How about this?

26:51.600 --> 26:54.200
I'll find a hotel nearby for you,
and you can stay there for one night.

26:55.720 --> 26:57.840
- You pay?
- Of course, that works.

26:59.280 --> 27:00.800
There should be
plenty of budget hotels around here.

27:00.880 --> 27:02.040
I can't stay in cheap places.

27:08.320 --> 27:10.560
Then pick one that suits you.
I'll pay for it.

27:11.080 --> 27:13.160
Just find a place as soon as you can.

27:13.920 --> 27:15.880
You're handling this quite well.

27:15.960 --> 27:18.520
Someone like you probably
isn't used to sharing a place, right?

27:19.200 --> 27:20.640
Let's not make things worse.

27:21.240 --> 27:23.200
Moving all your stuff back and forth
would be such a bother.

27:23.280 --> 27:24.960
How do you know I don't like it?

27:25.560 --> 27:27.800
Isn't sharing a place
all about lacking money?

27:27.880 --> 27:30.600
Your financial situation is great.
You shouldn't settle for less.

27:32.240 --> 27:35.400
My house burned down,
and I spent all the money on repairs.

27:35.480 --> 27:36.600
So, no, I don't have any left.

27:37.480 --> 27:39.280
Don't you still own a restaurant bar?

27:39.360 --> 27:40.600
Honestly,

27:41.720 --> 27:42.800
it doesn't make much money.

27:47.920 --> 27:51.320
My schedule's really irregular.
I often work overtime.

27:51.400 --> 27:53.040
I'm afraid it might disturb your rest.

27:55.640 --> 27:58.600
Then I hope you'll be quieter
when you get back.

28:04.240 --> 28:06.000
- I have a cat too.
- What's wrong with a cat?

28:06.080 --> 28:08.200
Cats shed fur. They also meow a lot.

28:08.280 --> 28:11.520
Plus, it's a stray cat, not a house cat.
I'm worried it might scratch you.

28:14.320 --> 28:16.200
You don't like cats, do you?

28:17.720 --> 28:20.360
- I don't like them, that's true.
- See? I told you we're not suitable…

28:25.360 --> 28:27.040
We're not suitable to live together.

28:29.320 --> 28:32.720
We're of the opposite sex.
Living together isn't convenient.

28:33.560 --> 28:37.920
You probably don't want
to overthink everything

28:38.000 --> 28:40.120
and feel uncomfortable

28:40.720 --> 28:42.520
at home, right?

28:44.920 --> 28:46.040
Wen Yifan,

28:47.720 --> 28:50.280
- your attitude is quite interesting.
- What do you mean?

28:50.360 --> 28:54.240
Do you think I'm still hung up on you,
still trying to cling to you like before?

28:54.320 --> 28:57.800
- I didn't mean that.
- So, I'm that sentimental in your eyes?

29:02.560 --> 29:03.400
You misunderstood me.

29:09.200 --> 29:11.680
Anyway, I've already moved my things in.
I can't be bothered with it.

29:12.480 --> 29:13.520
Give me three months.

29:14.680 --> 29:16.480
After my house is done,
I'll move out right away.

29:16.560 --> 29:20.000
- But you have only one suitcase here.
- During these three months,

29:22.160 --> 29:23.560
please don't try to get close to me.

29:23.640 --> 29:25.840
Alright, stop making excuses.

29:29.040 --> 29:30.600
Could it be that I was wrong?

29:35.320 --> 29:36.560
The person who can't let go

29:37.560 --> 29:38.600
is you.

29:42.080 --> 29:43.760
How could that be?

29:43.840 --> 29:45.360
You're overthinking.
I wouldn't dare to try anything with you.

29:45.440 --> 29:48.600
The reason I'm saying all this
is just to make things clear.

29:48.680 --> 29:50.480
- Got it.
- Then, don't overthink it.

29:52.040 --> 29:53.280
How about…

29:54.040 --> 29:55.200
Enough. Got it.

29:55.880 --> 29:58.720
How about this? You stay here tonight.

30:00.760 --> 30:02.400
We'll both think about it.

30:02.480 --> 30:05.040
And we'll talk about it tomorrow
after I finish work.

30:07.240 --> 30:08.200
When do you finish work?

30:08.920 --> 30:09.800
Not sure.

30:09.880 --> 30:12.160
- I'll try to be back before eight.
- Okay.

30:14.840 --> 30:17.040
Then, how about you sleep with me tonight?

30:25.000 --> 30:27.400
Did you say that wrong,
or did you just speak your mind?

30:27.480 --> 30:29.240
What I mean is,

30:29.320 --> 30:31.720
you can sleep in the master bedroom.

30:34.760 --> 30:35.800
Good night.

30:43.720 --> 30:46.400
You really think
I am so mild and ordinary?

30:48.080 --> 30:50.480
You'll soon see how explosive I can be.

30:53.880 --> 30:57.000
LIN, LET'S SEE TOMORROW?

31:32.520 --> 31:33.400
Sang Yan.

31:54.280 --> 31:56.400
How could he leave the keys behind?

32:06.440 --> 32:10.520
WHERE DID YOU SLEEP LAST NIGHT?

32:12.680 --> 32:14.760
Fan, you've been waiting a long time, huh?

32:15.760 --> 32:17.640
Did you order? I'll order for you too.

32:17.720 --> 32:19.600
- Their ice cream is really good.
- Lin.

32:19.680 --> 32:20.520
Waiter, I want…

32:20.600 --> 32:22.120
Let's talk about
the new roommate situation.

32:36.280 --> 32:37.360
I just don't get it.

32:37.960 --> 32:39.680
What's wrong with sharing with Sang Yan?

32:39.760 --> 32:41.760
I've said it I want a female roommate.

32:41.840 --> 32:44.320
What's the big difference there?

32:45.720 --> 32:47.400
How did you promise me at first?

32:49.360 --> 32:52.280
Do you think
he still likes you just because

32:52.360 --> 32:53.800
of that "romantic interest" stuff?

32:54.640 --> 32:56.320
Keep it to yourself.

32:56.400 --> 32:58.120
I heard from Su Haoan

32:58.200 --> 33:00.680
that Sang Yan never had
a girlfriend in college.

33:00.760 --> 33:04.080
He hung out with a guy called Duan Jiaxu
all the time.

33:06.080 --> 33:08.720
Doesn't that have anything to do
with our talk?

33:08.800 --> 33:10.880
I just wanted to tell you

33:10.960 --> 33:13.680
there are lots of advantages
to sharing with a male roommate.

33:13.760 --> 33:17.400
He can help with heavy work.
He might even chip in more for rent.

33:17.480 --> 33:19.280
If you use his things,
he won't make a fuss.

33:19.360 --> 33:20.320
I don't need that, Lin.

33:22.080 --> 33:25.360
I had a previous boyfriend.
We started dating after being roommates.

33:25.440 --> 33:27.400
Even if it's not Sang Yan,

33:27.480 --> 33:29.440
I think you should also find
a male roommate.

33:30.040 --> 33:32.000
Maybe… you'll no longer be single.

33:33.240 --> 33:35.520
Does the client in the ad department
with the Ferrari

33:35.600 --> 33:36.600
know about your new roommate?

33:38.360 --> 33:42.040
Does he know that on New Year's Eve,
you went to the hot springs with someone

33:42.560 --> 33:43.720
who drives a Porsche?

33:44.560 --> 33:46.840
Or about your cousin
who's helping you find a job?

33:47.720 --> 33:49.960
They should all be pretty familiar
with each other

33:50.040 --> 33:51.040
because they're all your cousins, right?

33:52.600 --> 33:54.800
What do you mean by that?
What does that have to do with you?

33:54.880 --> 33:57.200
Since you think
sharing with Sang Yan is so great,

33:57.280 --> 33:58.160
why not go live with him?

33:58.840 --> 34:00.800
More cousins as roommates
wouldn't hurt you.

34:00.880 --> 34:02.800
Fine, Wen Yifan,

34:03.600 --> 34:05.480
I didn't expect you
to be so sharp-tongued.

34:08.280 --> 34:10.760
I'm done. You can go ahead
and order the ice cream now.

34:32.040 --> 34:33.480
A male roommate?

34:34.040 --> 34:35.480
You're acting so nervous.

34:35.560 --> 34:36.639
Seems like
there's something fishy going on.

34:36.719 --> 34:38.159
What fishy thing?

34:39.000 --> 34:40.960
I'm asking you!

34:41.040 --> 34:43.280
Is he young? Can I see a photo?

34:44.120 --> 34:45.840
His Moments are empty. No photos.

34:46.560 --> 34:47.760
Is the profile picture really him?

34:48.280 --> 34:49.280
Not really.

34:50.120 --> 34:52.600
Plus, he hasn't confirmed
whether he will actually move in.

34:53.400 --> 34:54.800
Well, let's try to get him to.

34:54.880 --> 34:57.560
If he's a good person,
at least he'll provide some protection.

35:15.040 --> 35:16.280
His character is definitely good.

35:16.360 --> 35:20.320
At least, until I agreed,
he was very respectful toward me.

35:22.480 --> 35:25.960
WHERE DID YOU SLEEP LAST NIGHT?

35:26.040 --> 35:27.720
Where should we talk today?

35:28.240 --> 35:31.000
Should we find a place
or talk at the house?

35:31.080 --> 35:32.000
WHERE SHOULD WE TALK TODAY?

35:32.080 --> 35:33.360
SHOULD WE FIND A PLACE
OR TALK AT THE HOUSE?

35:33.440 --> 35:36.680
8 P.M. AT YOUR PLACE

36:10.080 --> 36:13.160
I'm dressing so casually. Is it suitable?

36:30.800 --> 36:32.200
The door wasn't locked.

36:38.000 --> 36:39.920
Why didn't you bring the keys last night?

36:41.400 --> 36:43.600
I saw you didn't sleep in your room.

36:43.680 --> 36:44.960
Where did you sleep?

36:46.440 --> 36:47.560
At a hotel.

36:49.560 --> 36:50.480
A five-star one.

36:54.480 --> 36:56.200
How much was it per night?

36:57.080 --> 36:58.520
Aren't you here to talk?

37:01.760 --> 37:02.640
Let's talk.

37:12.080 --> 37:13.560
Have you made up your mind?

37:15.080 --> 37:16.360
Have you thought it through?

37:19.800 --> 37:20.760
I…

37:22.360 --> 37:23.680
I agree for you to move in.

37:29.520 --> 37:31.600
Honestly, my requirements
for a roommate aren't that high.

37:32.320 --> 37:35.920
I only hope its character is good,
and we won't interfere with each other.

37:39.200 --> 37:40.680
Are you that trusting of me?

37:41.200 --> 37:42.480
There's nothing I'm worried about.

37:42.560 --> 37:44.720
But I'm a bit worried about you.

37:48.400 --> 37:50.440
There's nothing
that should make you worry.

37:50.520 --> 37:52.320
If there's no problem,
let's talk about the details.

37:52.400 --> 37:53.240
For example?

37:53.320 --> 37:55.400
Before leaving,
Lin gave me the landlord's WeChat.

37:55.480 --> 37:58.400
The house is rented under her name.
The lease has six months left.

37:58.480 --> 37:59.320
Got it.

38:01.000 --> 38:03.720
Then, about this house,
the rent is 7,000 a month.

38:05.760 --> 38:07.280
If you take the master bedroom,

38:07.800 --> 38:10.680
the bigger room with a private bathroom,

38:12.080 --> 38:13.720
is 4,000 okay?

38:16.680 --> 38:17.600
Sounds reasonable.

38:20.400 --> 38:21.640
- So, that works?
- Yes.

38:25.360 --> 38:27.840
Now, about the deposit,
it's one month's rent.

38:27.920 --> 38:29.240
Right now, I'm covering it.

38:29.320 --> 38:32.440
- If you move in, we'll split it evenly.
- No problem.

38:33.320 --> 38:34.160
Okay.

38:34.240 --> 38:36.800
Then, there are the utilities
and other fees.

38:36.880 --> 38:38.080
My idea is

38:38.160 --> 38:40.240
we both contribute a little to the fund,

38:40.320 --> 38:41.360
so we don't need to calculate it
every month.

38:41.440 --> 38:43.240
Just give me the total when needed.

38:46.000 --> 38:46.880
Anything else?

38:46.960 --> 38:49.360
That's about it for the money part.

38:49.880 --> 38:50.720
Okay.

38:50.800 --> 38:52.840
Then I'll send you
the details and total later.

38:52.920 --> 38:53.760
Alright.

38:55.800 --> 38:56.840
Wait a minute.

38:57.480 --> 39:00.680
Because I don't have much experience
sharing a place with a man

39:01.440 --> 39:04.320
and the past experiences
weren't that great,

39:05.720 --> 39:06.760
even though you'll only be here
for three months,

39:06.840 --> 39:08.800
I think we should discuss
our expectations in advance.

39:08.880 --> 39:09.920
Is that okay?

39:11.000 --> 39:12.880
No problem. You go first.

39:16.440 --> 39:17.640
For example…

39:20.040 --> 39:21.520
For example…

39:23.680 --> 39:26.720
For example, keep quiet
when the other roommate is resting.

39:27.880 --> 39:28.920
Alright.

39:37.360 --> 39:39.040
The second is to maintain cleanliness.

39:39.120 --> 39:41.400
Whoever makes a mess, cleans it up.

39:41.480 --> 39:43.120
Got it. Understood.

39:45.920 --> 39:47.760
The third point is…

39:52.840 --> 39:56.360
The third one is,
no nudity in public spaces.

40:06.280 --> 40:07.640
You really wish, huh?

40:12.400 --> 40:13.240
The fourth?

40:19.800 --> 40:20.800
The fourth…

40:21.320 --> 40:22.840
and the last point is…

40:22.920 --> 40:24.280
If you want to bring a friend home,

40:24.360 --> 40:25.800
you must get
the other roommate's permission,

40:25.880 --> 40:27.680
whether they're men or women.

40:29.640 --> 40:30.680
Do you have a girlfriend?

40:34.360 --> 40:36.640
What I mean is, if you have a girlfriend,

40:36.720 --> 40:39.280
let her know in advance
about our co-living situation

40:39.360 --> 40:40.680
to avoid any misunderstandings.

40:48.120 --> 40:49.440
I don't have a girlfriend.

40:49.520 --> 40:51.480
But don't get too happy yet.

40:52.000 --> 40:53.480
I just don't want to date.

40:55.880 --> 40:56.720
I see.

41:03.560 --> 41:04.680
Fine.

41:04.760 --> 41:07.480
Then, if you start dating
during our time living together,

41:07.560 --> 41:08.840
we'll talk about it.

41:10.160 --> 41:12.760
Of course, if I start dating,
I'll let you know too.

41:12.840 --> 41:13.680
Not interested.

41:17.360 --> 41:19.520
That's all I have to say. Anything to add?

41:28.240 --> 41:29.360
We'll talk about it later.

41:34.440 --> 41:35.680
I'll take this room?

41:49.520 --> 41:52.520
Before Lin left,
this place was already cleaned.

42:03.880 --> 42:06.760
Check if there is anything else
you're not happy with.

42:06.840 --> 42:08.360
I'll fix it.

42:13.440 --> 42:16.880
This is the kitchen.
There are lots of cabinets.

42:18.120 --> 42:18.960
There are two levels here.

42:19.040 --> 42:20.120
- We can each take one level.
- Alright.

42:20.200 --> 42:22.040
You're taller,
so you can take the top level.

42:22.120 --> 42:25.520
- Sounds good.
- This one here is the dishwasher.

42:25.600 --> 42:27.800
I'm familiar with dishwashers.

42:28.320 --> 42:30.560
- I know how to use the oven too.
- Sorry.

42:33.600 --> 42:35.880
That's the range hood. I know.

42:36.800 --> 42:38.680
No need to go into so much details.
I've checked this place before.

42:44.720 --> 42:46.080
This is the guest bathroom.

42:46.600 --> 42:49.440
Since your room has an en-suite,
this one is for me.

42:52.960 --> 42:53.960
May I come in?

42:55.480 --> 42:56.680
Sure.

42:56.760 --> 42:58.760
But my room is a bit small.

43:00.200 --> 43:01.320
Feel free to look around.

43:19.800 --> 43:21.560
This room's pretty good. I'll take it.

43:23.680 --> 43:25.040
Why?

43:25.760 --> 43:28.560
Your room has a balcony
and a private bathroom.

43:28.640 --> 43:30.840
But this room is a bit small,
and the lighting isn't great.

43:30.920 --> 43:32.480
Although it's smaller,

43:33.840 --> 43:34.760
please move into that one.

43:35.800 --> 43:38.160
Do you think 4,000 is too expensive?

43:38.240 --> 43:40.080
But 3,000 is already my limit.

43:40.160 --> 43:42.640
You're still at 3,000.
You don't need to pay more.

43:43.320 --> 43:44.600
That's not right.

43:45.120 --> 43:47.800
How can you pay more
and get the smaller room? This won't work.

43:47.880 --> 43:49.800
Whether the room is good is my decision,

43:50.440 --> 43:51.720
not the house's.

43:54.280 --> 43:56.720
But even an idiot knows
to stay in a good room.

43:56.800 --> 43:57.840
So, I'm not an idiot.

44:30.160 --> 44:32.400
Is he purposely giving me the bigger room?

45:12.040 --> 45:14.120
I'm sorry. I heard that your place

45:14.200 --> 45:16.240
was hit the hardest by the fire, correct?

45:16.320 --> 45:17.320
So what?

45:17.400 --> 45:22.240
THE STORY IS NOT OVER YET…

45:22.320 --> 45:24.520
What I mean is,
there's nothing valuable in my home,

45:24.600 --> 45:25.480
so it's fine.

46:22.680 --> 46:26.400
WEN YIFAN: I'LL COME FIND YOU

46:27.600 --> 46:29.280
WHERE ARE YOU?
CALL ME BACK WHEN YOU SEE THE MESSAGE

46:29.360 --> 46:30.520
DID YOU GET YOUR ACCEPTANCE LETTER?

46:30.600 --> 46:31.520
REPLY TO THE MESSAGE
I'LL COME FIND YOU

49:21.120 --> 49:22.440
HUGE THANKS TO EVERYONE INVOLVED
AND TO ALL THE FANS OF THE FIRST FROST!

49:22.520 --> 49:23.360
TREAT YOURSELF WELL
AND THE WORLD WILL HOLD MORE LOVE FOR YOU!
